“—Щharchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/lang-guide/chapters/types/basic_types/datetime.mdЩ@6471a48997da1dbd7e474e5f7f7242cfecc130bf7930c7275dd49f0aecae3b2bЁDatetime‘ЁDatetimeЪ¶Description:

Represents a specific point in time using international standard date time descriptors
Annotation:

``datetime``

Literal syntax:

RFC 3339
Date-only: 
``2022-02-02``

Date and time (GMT): 
``2022-02-02T14:30:00``

Date and time including timezone offset: 
``2022-02-02T14:30:00+05:00``

Casts:

[link: /commands/docs/into_datetime.md] ``into datetime``
See also:

[link: /book/types_of_data.md#dates] Types of Data - Dates
