—Щharchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/lang-guide/chapters/types/basic_types/datetime.mdЩ@e36376178dcc5ff03332c8a36c0d03dbc7f1954ad2eedf83c699c40b3ad7205dЁDatetime‘№Additional language notesЩ™Dates and times are held together in the 
